Package: ggalign
Title: Align Multiple 'ggplot' Objects
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Yun", "Peng", , "yunyunp96@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2801-3332"))
Description: This package is an extension of ggplot2 that aligns multiple ggplot objects
    along their axes in the same order. It is highly beneficial for organizing plots
    that involve changing the order of data. 
